<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.2">
<l>cikkeṉac ciṟitō riṭamum puṟappaṭāt taṉṉuḷḷē yulakuka</l>
<l>ḷokkavē viḻuṅkip pukuntāṉ pukuntataṟpiṉ</l>
<l>mikka ñāṉa veḷḷac cuṭarviḷakkāyt tuḷakkaṟ ṟamutamā yeṅkum</l>
<l>pakkanōk kaṟiyāṉeṉ paintāmaraik kaṇṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tightly, in his interior from which not one place gets out even a little, equally</l>
<l>swallowing the worlds he has entered. After entering,</l>
<l>being a glowing lamp with an increasing flood of knowledge, sorrow ending, as ambrosia, everywhere,</l>
<l>he does not know of looking aside, my fresh lotus-eyed Kṛṣṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
